Title : Maria of Romania
Text : '''Maria of Romania''' or similar names can refer to:

* [[Marie of Romania|Queen Maria of Romania]] (1875–1938), wife of King Ferdinand I and grandmother of King Michael I
* [[Maria of Yugoslavia|Princess Maria of Romania]] (1900–1961), queen of Yugoslavia and daughter of King Ferdinand I
* [[Princess Maria of Romania (1870–1874)|Princess Maria of Romania]] (1870–1874), daughter of King Carol I
* [[Princess Marie of Romania|Princess Maria of Romania]] (born 1964), daughter of King Michael I

